Zap Fitness
Lacy Morrow
http:// student.cs.appstate.edu/morrowtl/zap/
The purpose of this site is to provide a web application to allow coaches a channel to connect to the runners they coach. They may provide runners with weekly workouts which may be viewed and uupdated by the runners.
Home Page
Runner calendar
Coach/Runner Dashboard
Login/Logout Page
Submit workout page

A fading text shadow, a custom header bar interface, css gradients and the image slideshow are all unique elements of my site